      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-01098'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040719_GCR_351' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 120 [<span class="italic">Duty to assume responsibility for schemes following application or notification</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-01099'>
