            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_51gc' title='Col. 51GC &mdash; HL Deb 19 July 2004 vol 664 c51GC' name='column_51gc' href='#column_51gc' rel='bookmark'>51GC</a>
            various such bodies. She also mentioned foreign employers. Can she give us an example to satisfy my curiosity?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0664P0-01145'>
